title: tensorboard ImportError: cannot import name 'run_main'
body_html:
I install the tensorflow on Mac from source.
but when I run the tensorboard,and got a error like this

Pro-2:Desktop xxh$ tensorboard
Traceback (most recent call last):
File "/Users/xxh/anaconda3/bin/tensorboard", line 7, in
from tensorboard.main import run_main
ImportError: cannot import name 'run_main'`

How to fix it?
